I also shed clarity on the situation as a whole and what our intentions and actions

186
00:10:16,773 --> 00:10:17,593
are moving forward.

187
00:10:18,854 --> 00:10:23,498
I go on to reassure him and acknowledge that his points are valid and that we will try

188
00:10:23,538 --> 00:10:24,619
to do something about them.

189
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:29,983
