190
00:10:33,798 --> 00:10:35,880
In the last section of my reply to Daryl,

191
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:38,541
I approach problem solving by taking ownership

192
00:10:38,561 --> 00:10:42,143
of the situation and giving an honest, clear answer

193
00:10:42,183 --> 00:10:43,223
to the best of my ability.

194
00:10:44,144 --> 00:10:46,165
I attempt to consolidate the relationship further

195
00:10:46,185 --> 00:10:46,925
and build rapport.

196
00:10:47,686 --> 00:10:49,587
This is evidenced by my final statement,

197
00:10:49,667 --> 00:10:50,467
take care of yourself.

198
00:10:51,447 --> 00:10:53,509
Connecting and showing an element of care

199
00:10:53,629 --> 00:10:55,389
is humanizing your brand and product.

200
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:58,591
Part of community engagement is connecting

201
00:10:58,631 --> 00:11:00,592
with individuals and your community as a whole.

202
00:11:02,105 --> 00:11:06,671
